    public abstract class AbstractFieldProbe<T>
extends AbstractProbe<T>

      • readField

        protected def readField() : T 
        Description copied from class: AbstractFieldProbe
        Read the value from the associated field. This function is not thread-safe by itself.
        Returns:
        the value of the field, or null if the value is evaluated to null or the type of the value is not compatible with the one replied by AbstractProbe.getType().

      • writeField

        protected def writeField(value : T) : T 
        Description copied from class: AbstractFieldProbe
        Write the value to the associated field.
        Parameters:
        value - is the new value to write into the field.
        Returns:
        the value of the field before its change, or null if the old value is evaluated to null or the type of the old value is not compatible with the one replied by AbstractProbe.getType().
